ORCH-005: Agent Registry -- registration and capability declaration. PR #31 merged. AgentRegistry class with 6 ITOM agent definitions, capability search, persistence. 40 new tests (243 total, 95% coverage).
ORCH-006: Agent health checking and status monitoring. PR #32 merged. AgentHealthChecker with TTL cache, bulk checks, history, MCP tools. 28 new tests (271 total, 91% coverage).

ORCH-007: Agent configuration file and dynamic loading. PR #33 merged. AgentConfigLoader with agents.json schema, Pydantic validation, runtime reload, diff detection. 36 new tests (307 total, 90% coverage).

Phase 2: Agent Registry -- COMPLETE. 3/3 tickets done. Milestone M-2 achieved: All 6 ITOM agents registered with capabilities, health checks functional, get_agent_registry and get_agent_status MCP tools operational.

ORCH-026: Add FastAPI HTTP server layer alongside FastMCP. PR #37 merged. http_server.py with create_app() factory, CORS middleware, api/routes.py with health/agents-status/agent-details endpoints. 23 new tests (330 total, all passing).

ORCH-028: GET /api/health and GET /api/agents/status endpoints. PR #38 merged. Enhanced routes.py with force_check query param, GET /api/agents/{id}, GET /api/agents/{id}/health. 8 new tests (338 total passing).

ORCH-008: Task Router -- domain-based routing engine. PR #39 merged. router.py with 4-method priority routing (explicit>rules>domain>capability), RoutingRule/RoutingDecision models, default rules for all 6 ITOM domains, route_task MCP tool. 38 new tests (376 total passing).

ORCH-009: Task execution and result handling. PR #40 merged. executor.py with TaskExecutor dispatch lifecycle, timeout handling, exponential backoff retry, pluggable dispatch handlers, execution history persistence. get_execution_history MCP tool. 22 new tests (398 total passing).

ORCH-027: POST /api/chat endpoint for message routing. PR #41 merged. api/chat.py with ChatRequest/ChatResponse Pydantic models, process_chat_message() routing via TaskRouter+TaskExecutor. POST /api/chat in routes.py with 400/502/504 error handling. 17 new tests (415 total passing).

Phase 2b: HTTP API Layer -- COMPLETE. 3/3 tickets done. Milestone M-2b achieved: FastAPI server running on port 8000 with /api/health, /api/chat, /api/agents/status, /api/agents/{id}, /api/agents/{id}/health endpoints. Chat-ui integration unblocked.
Auto mode session: 5 completed, 0 skipped. Stop reason: scope_exhausted. PRs merged: #37, #38, #39, #40, #41. Phase 2b complete. Phase 3 at 67% (2/3 tickets). 108 new tests added (415 total).
